These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-6-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, tea
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, tulip, amaryllis
City: san-francisco, berlin, venice
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, scientific, time-travel
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, volleyball
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, ritmeester, dunhill
 1. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
 2. the person drinking juice is in the middle##1
 3. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 5. the person watching family movies is not the person drinking lemonade##6
 6. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
 7. the person watching scientific movies is in an even position##4
 8. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
 9. the person traveling to berlin is between the person who's sport is climbing and the dunhill-smoker##2
10. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | tea        | juice        | lemonade    |
| Hobby         | lily    | amaryllis       | tulip      |
| Job           | venice | berlin | san-francisco |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | scientific   | time-travel |
| Music-Genre   | climbing       | volleyball      | sailing      |
| Nationality   | game   | ritmeester      | dunhill     |

