 2. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the person who growsaconite##5
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person eating banana##1
 4. the prince-smoker is the person driving the tram##1
 5. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is in the middle##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
 8. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 9. the person who growsrose is not the bongani-smoker##6
10. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | tea         | 7up        | mirinda       |
| Hobby         | banana | kiwi    | broccoli   |
