The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, july, june
 1. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
 2. the person playing backgammon is not the person who growsrose##6
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
 4. the person who growszinnia is not the person playing backgammon##6
 5. the police-officer is not the person playing mah-jongg##6
 6. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person watching thriller movies and the person who's birthday is in november##2
 8. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
 9. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the dancer is between the person who's birthday is in november and the bartender##2
11. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
12. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
