.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-6-17::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, bellflower, daisy
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, grapefruit, potato
3 different pets are kept: goat, horse, frog
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, gardening, writing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, lacrosse, water-polo
House: farmhouse, futuristic, cottage
 1. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
 2. the cottage house is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the person eating potato##5
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the futuristic house##1
 5. the person eating potato is on the far left##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is not the person who's sport is water-polo##6
 7. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 9. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
11. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the farmhouse house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |      3      |
| Beverage      | daisy | bellflower          | orchid |
| Food          | potato        | grapefruit     | cauliflower |
| Job           | goat        | horse | frog   |
| Movie-Genre   | magic-tricks         | gardening          | writing |
| Sport         | lacrosse      | basketball     | water-polo  |
| Transport     | futuristic       | farmhouse            | cottage       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-6-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, water
3 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, mah-jongg
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, baking, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, blues, country
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, water-polo, weightlifting
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, june, december
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is not the person drinking milk##6
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is not the fan ambient##6
 3. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
 4. the fan country is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
 6. the fan ambient is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 9. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
11. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
12. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Food          | milk   | 7up | water |
| Job           | backgammon    | mah-jongg  | monopoly |
| Movie-Genre   | photography     | baking | sudoku |
| Music-Genre   | country       | blues   | ambient    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | cricket | water-polo |
| Transport     | march      | june    | december        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-6-19::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, september, may
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, amber, azure
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, polish, spanish
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, satire, animation
City: new-york, colone, prague
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, train, trike
 1. the polish is not the person who's birthday is in december##6
 2. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the bus and the person traveling to colone##2
 3. the spanish is not the person watching crime movies##6
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is not the person driving the train##6
 5. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5
 7. the person driving the bus is the spanish##1
 8. the person driving the train is the person traveling to colone##1
 9. the mexican is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
10. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
11. the person driving the trike is not the person traveling to prague##6
12. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |
| Beverage      | september | december      | may          |
| Job           | amber | fuchsia | azure |
| Nationality   | polish      | mexican  | spanish        |
| Pet           | crime         | animation    | satire            |
| Sport         | colone      | new-york     | prague         |
| Transport     | train       | trike    | bus            |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-6-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, photography, drawing
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, amaryllis, tulip
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, folk, hip-hop
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, security-guard, accountant
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, parkour, volleyball
House: craftsman, townhouse, cape-cod
 1. the fan classical is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the right of the townhouse house##5
 3. the accountant is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
 4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
 5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 6. the person who growspoppy is the craftsman house##1
 7. the security-guard is on the right of the fan hip-hop##1
 8. the person who growstulip is in the middle##1
 9. the accountant is not the person who's hobby is photography##6
10. the fan folk is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |
| Beverage      | drawing     | photography      | collecting       |
| Food          | amaryllis   | tulip | poppy  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | folk       | classical |
| Pet           | designer        | security-guard        | accountant     |
| Sport         | parkour    | volleyball | biathlon  |
| Transport     | townhouse | cape-cod      | craftsman  |

 